2500|$|A vacuum toilet is a {{flush toilet}} that {{requires}} very little <b>flushing</b> <b>water</b> and {{is connected to}} a vacuum sewer system. For example, [...] they are used on planes (aircraft lavatories) and on trains (passenger train toilets).|$|R
